snippet.title: Cheddar Beach 0: Party on Mango St. - Coming Soon Trailer
snippet.description:
Cheddar Beach 0: Party on Mango St., a visual novel coming soon to mobile and Steam. Join Hamston and The Homies as they look for a crackin' party on a Friday night!

Take a trip to Cheddar Beach in this interactive visual novel! Join Hamston & The Homies as they search for a crackin’ house party on a Friday night, in a world inspired by LA in the early 90’s.

Find out more at http://cheddarbeach.com.

Created by Bryson Whiteman.

Created by Sokay (https://www.sokay.net)
